{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"LDC4","author":"Weedust"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"18f1fcfb-27a0-5b51-8a78-c5b5545942c6","excerpt":"\n任何极端情况下，都存在性能优化。  \n页面上DOM只要一多，即便是性能怪兽的V8也会卡。  \n本案例的本质就是局部可见是有限的，可以限制在不卡的范围。  \n\n","html":"<p>任何极端情况下，都存在性能优化。<br>\n页面上DOM只要一多，即便是性能怪兽的V8也会卡。<br>\n本案例的本质就是局部可见是有限的，可以限制在不卡的范围。  </p>\n<!-- more -->\n<h2>背景</h2>\n<p>todo</p>\n<h2>参考资料</h2>\n<p>从时间线列举了一些跟虚拟列表有关的文章和库</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/bvaughn/react-virtualized\">React Virtualized</a> |\n<a href=\"https://github.com/Akryum/vue-virtual-scroller\">Vue Virtual Scroll</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://developers.google.com/web/updates/2016/07/infinite-scroller\">Complexities of an Infinite Scroller</a><br>\nby developers.google.com/web</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://itsze.ro/blog/2017/04/09/infinite-list-and-react.html\">Infinite List and React</a><br>\nby itsze.ro/blog</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/26022258\">聊聊前端开发中的长列表</a><br>\nby 知乎专栏 - Furybean</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/34585166\">再谈前端虚拟列表的实现</a><br>\nby 知乎专栏 - Furybean</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/dwqs/blog/issues/70\">浅说虚拟列表的实现原理</a><br>\nby github - dwqs</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://juejin.im/post/5d76f469f265da039a28aff7\">「前端进阶」高性能渲染十万条数据(时间分片)</a><br>\nby 掘金 - 云中桥</p>\n<p>[「前端进阶」高性能渲染十万条数据(虚拟列表)<br>\n<a href=\"https://juejin.im/post/5db684ddf265da4d495c40e5\">https://juejin.im/post/5db684ddf265da4d495c40e5</a><br>\nby 掘金 - 云中桥</p>\n<h2>实际场景</h2>","frontmatter":{"title":"虚拟列表/树","date":"2019-11-15 09:23:32","tags":["虚拟列表","虚拟树"],"category":"实践","draft":true}},"allNavigationJson":{"edges":[{"node":{"name":"分类","link":"/cats"}},{"node":{"name":"标签","link":"/tags"}},{"node":{"name":"关于","link":"/about"}}]},"allGitalkJson":{"edges":[{"node":{"clientID":"49e26d4dd7cf72ebb64d","clientSecret":"e593383921b7f8ef0b08db7fc8c109828a8e50d1","repo":"blog","owner":"ldc4","admin":["ldc4"]}}]}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/virtual-tree/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/vue/"},"frontmatter":{"